  <title>CMake-&cmake-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The CMake package contains a modern toolset used for generating Makefiles.
      It is a successor of the auto-generated <command>configure</command>
      script and aims to be platform- and compiler-independent. A significant
      user of CMake is KDE since version 4.
    </para>

